snippet.textDisplay:
It's been years since I've been listening to Coke Studio Pakistan and I used to wonder  why despite this much diversity in music, we are  failing to see the same with Coke Studio India. 

I'm so proud today, that we are actually showcasing what we have, to the world. I would like to appreciate everyone who brought this wave of change in Coke Studio India.


Also noticed the caption has given credits to every single person in the team.


I'm so amazed with all the music that has been put up since last few months. With the type of diversity our country has, I'm sure there is so much more coming.
